# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# VDAP Protocol — .gitignore (Security Hardened)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# GOLDEN RULE: NEVER commit secrets, keys, or credentials.
# If in doubt, add it here FIRST.
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Secrets & Environment Variables ──────────────────────────────────
# CRITICAL: These files contain private keys, RPC URLs, API keys, etc.
# Committing any of these is an IRREVERSIBLE security breach.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.keystore
*.jks
*.cert
*.crt
*.csr
mnemonic.txt
secret.txt
.secret
.secrets
credentials.json
serviceAccountKey.json
keyfile.json

# ── Wallet / Blockchain Secrets ──────────────────────────────────────
# Keystores, private keys, and recovery phrases
wallets/
keystores/
*.keystore
*.wallet

